survey_response.review_text: I had a consultation with Dr. Amita for my test reports of a comprehensive health checkup. Dr. Amita identified the right issues, asked relevant questions about the symptoms and prescribed treatment and follow-ups. She also reassured not to worry about certain parameters with explanation. She answered all my questions patiently and in a friendly and approachable manner. I am happy with my consultation with Dr. Amita.

Dr Amita was very kind to me on the online consultation. My entire family was down with covid and I had consulted her for my daughter specifically. She patiently replied  to all my queries. She assured that things would become better and that faith helped us sail through the situation. Thank you doctor

Had a good experience with doctor. she suggested antiviral for my prolonged fever and all the tests. The medicines worked best and I started feeling quickly. would definitely recommend her. Also, she explained and listen to the problem really patiently and well

I had a discussion regarding my health checkup report. The doctor was quick to diagnose the basic issue and gave me clear consultation on what is to be treated and how to change my lifestyle. She suggested few tests and was also quick to give consultation post the submission on new test. I strongly recommend Dr. Amita. Thanks for your help.

I did not have a very good experience with Dr. Amrita Mody. I had got a full body check done and had consulted her to check my report and give me feedback about the same. I shared 2 reports with her and she referred to only one. I kept telling her that she has not given me any feedback about thyroid and my Vitamin deficiency so she asked me to share the report again and even before I could share the report the marked the session as completed and since the session is marked as completed I cannot call her and the only way of communication is the chat window. Now it's been 3-4 hours and I am just waiting for her to response and still my queries are unanswered. I felt that the online patients are not being treated with equal importantance and urgency.

It was our first interaction through Practo. We are so thankful to Dr Amita Mody she was good and helped us understand the ailment better. The online consultation saved us the hassle of going to the clinic. It not only saved time but also made economic sense. Thank you Practo and Dr Amita.
